comments: Hart (NOP) makes incidental contact to Harden's (HOU) arm after the release of the ball on his jump shot attempt.
House Jr.'s (HOU) leg makes incidental contact to Williamson's (NOP) front during his attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Gordon (HOU) makes contact with Hart's (NOP) arm prior to making contact with the ball.
Gordon (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during Holiday's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
House Jr. (HOU) makes marginal contact with Hart (NOP) during the rebound.
Ingram (NOP) makes contact to Westbrook's (HOU) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) receives the pass and takes a legal step before the shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) goes to not through Tucker (HOU) after the release of the pass.
Harden (HOU) makes contact to Williamson's (NOP) body while he is airborne and the contact affects his FOM.
Holiday (NOP) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
